Package com.xd.cps2002.map

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BasicMap
    The BasicMap class is a concrete implementation of the Map class, and it contains the implementations of the Map.generate() and Map.isPlayable() functions particular to this type of map.
    BasicMapTest
    This class contains unit tests used to test both the methods of the abstract Map class and the concrete BasicMap class.
    Map
    The Map abstract class provides a common interface for all the different types of map types.
    MapCreator
    The MapCreator class is used to create different types of Map objects.
    MapCreatorTest
    This class contains unit tests used to test the methods of the MapCreator class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TileType
    The TileType enum defines the different types of tiles used in different maps.
